      • DO_BATCH_JOB

        public static boolean DO_BATCH_JOB
        A flag to indicate, whether batch jobs are currently allowed. This is set by the SettingsWindow, breaking the model view control pattern a little. It is a static flag rather than a flag in every OutputConfiguration, because it is the same for all requests that are started at a time, and saves some space in the OutputConfigurations.
